      <div xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313">
        <head xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Hd1e99" type="question-title">De advocatis</head>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-d1e102">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e112" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Rd1e104">Gregorius, <title>super Ezechielem</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e112">Justus advocatus injustas causas nullo modo
              accipit, nec verba dare pro injustitia consentit.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-d1e117">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e127" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Rd1e119">Gregorius, super illud <title>Job</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e127">
              <!--<i>-->De convallibus ista rapientes, cum singula reperissent, ad ea cum clamore
              currebant<!--</i>-->: In valle repertis singulis cum clamore occurrere, ex subortis
              causarum occasionibus, etiam pro parva stirpe litigare.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-d1e136">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e146" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Rd1e138">Augustinus, <title>de Verbis Domini</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e146">Usque adeo cupiditatis inolevit malum, ut jam ex
              consuetudine vendantur leges, corrumpantur jura, sententia ipsa venalis sit, et nulla
              jam causa possit esse sine causa.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-d1e151">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e161" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Rd1e153">Bernardus, <title>de Consideratione</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e161">Quotidie perstrepunt in palatio leges, sed
              Justiniani, non Domini.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-d1e167">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e177" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Rd1e169">Bernardus, <title>de Consideratione</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e177">Certe <!--<i>-->lex Domini immaculata, convertens
              animas<!--</i>-->. Hae autem non tam leges, quam lites sunt, et cavillationes
              subvertentes judicium.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-d1e186">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e196" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Rd1e188">Bernardus, <title>de Consideratione</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e196">Miror, quemadmodum religiosae aures tuae audire
              sustinent hujusmodi disputationes advocatorum, et pugnas verborum, quae magis ad
              subversionem, quam ad inventionem proficiunt veritatis. Corrige pravum morem, et
              praecide linguas vaniloquas, et labia dolosa claude.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-d1e201">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e211" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Rd1e203">Bernardus, <title>de Consideratione</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e211">Advocati sunt, qui docuerunt linguas suas loqui
              mendacium; diserti, adversus justitiam; eruditi, pro falsitate; sapientes sunt, ut
              faciant malum; eloquentes, ut impugnent verum.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-d1e216">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e226" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Rd1e218">Bernardus, <title>de Consideratione</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e226">Iniqua omnis appellatio, ad quam justitiae inopia
              non coegit. Appellare, non ut graves, sed si graveris, licet.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-d1e231">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e241" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Rd1e233">Bernardus, <title>de Consideratione</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e7313-Qd1e241">Qui non gravatus appellat, liquet quia aut
              gravare intendit, aut tempus redimere.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
      </div>
